    "helpHtml": "<h3>🎯 Objective</h3>\n        <ul>\n          <li>Start from the <strong>access point</strong> (green) and move along adjacent nodes to the <strong>data core</strong> (cyan).</li>\n          <li>Each step ICE patrols; stepping on ICE or sharing its cell costs integrity.</li>\n          <li>Complete the breach before the timer hits zero with integrity remaining.</li>\n        </ul>\n        <h3>🧩 Node Types</h3>\n        <div class=\"legend\">\n          <span style=\"color:#34d399\">● Access point</span>\n          <span style=\"color:#22d3ee\">◆ Data core</span>\n          <span style=\"color:#ef4444\">▲ ICE</span>\n          <span style=\"color:#6b7280\">■ Locked node</span>\n          <span style=\"color:#f97316\">⬡ Firewall</span>\n        </div>\n        <h3>⚡ Scoring & Combos</h3>\n        <ul>\n          <li>Consecutive safe moves build a <strong>combo chain</strong> — higher combos score more.</li>\n          <li>Remaining time and move efficiency affect final score and S/A/B/C/D grades.</li>\n          <li>Difficulty changes ICE speed and time limit.</li>\n        </ul>\n        <h3>🕹 Controls</h3>\n        <ul>\n          <li>Click an adjacent (up/down/left/right) passable node to move.</li>\n          <li>Firewalls need an extra step to breach (costs 2 moves).</li>\n          <li>Undo last move (2 per level).</li>\n        </ul>",
