      "helpHtml": "<h3>🎯 Objective</h3>\n        <p>At the center of the industrial base sits a <strong>core fission reactor</strong>. Alien machines pour in from the map edges and rush the core in straight lines. Build towers, destroy enemies, and protect the core until every wave is cleared.</p>\n        <h3>👾 Enemy Types</h3>\n        <ul>\n                  <li><strong>Scout (red):</strong> Fast, low HP</li>\n                  <li><strong>Swarm (orange):</strong> Small, numerous, very fast</li>\n                  <li><strong>Phantom (cyan):</strong> High evasion, medium HP</li>\n                  <li><strong>Heavy (gray):</strong> Slow, high HP</li>\n                  <li><strong>Shield (blue):</strong> 50% damage reduction — focus fire</li>\n                  <li><strong>Brood (green):</strong> Spawns mini-scouts on death</li>\n                  <li><strong>Elite (purple):</strong> Medium speed, high reward</li>\n                  <li><strong>Titan (dark):</strong> Boss-tier — huge HP and core damage</li>\n        </ul>\n        <h3>🏭 Tower Types</h3>\n        <ul>\n                  <li><strong>Gun (50):</strong> Fast fire rate, early clear</li>\n                  <li><strong>Laser (120):</strong> Continuous beam, high single-target DPS</li>\n                  <li><strong>Frost (150):</strong> Slows enemies, zone control</li>\n                  <li><strong>Sniper (180):</strong> Long range, high burst</li>\n                  <li><strong>Mortar (200):</strong> Area blasts vs dense packs</li>\n                  <li><strong>Tesla (250):</strong> Chain lightning, multi-target</li>\n                  <li><strong>Rocket (320):</strong> Homing missiles, splash damage</li>\n        </ul>\n        <h3>⚙️ Tactical Skills</h3>\n        <ul>\n                  <li><strong>Core Fission (200 ore):</strong> Pulse deals 40% max HP to all enemies</li>\n                  <li><strong>Tower Overdrive (150 ore):</strong> All towers fire ×2 for 8 seconds</li>\n                  <li><strong>Airdrop Supply:</strong> +90 ore every 3 waves</li>\n        </ul>\n        <h3>⚙️ Difficulties</h3>\n        <ul>\n                  <li><strong>Easy:</strong> 8 waves, generous ore, slower enemies — learn the build rhythm</li>\n                  <li><strong>Normal:</strong> 12 waves, tighter resources, more mixed formations</li>\n                  <li><strong>Hard:</strong> 15 waves, fast raids, bosses more often</li>\n                  <li><strong>Extreme:</strong> 18 waves, tight economy, dense formations — precise control</li>\n        </ul>\n        <h3>⚙️ Controls</h3>\n        <ul>\n                  <li><strong>Click / touch map:</strong> Place the selected tower (tap cells on mobile)</li>\n                  <li><strong>Start:</strong> After deploying, press Start to enter battle</li>\n                  <li><strong>Next wave:</strong> Manually start the next raid</li>\n                  <li><strong>Auto next:</strong> Auto-continue after a wave is cleared</li>\n        </ul>",
