      "helpBack": "Back",
      "helpHtml": "<h3>🎯 Objective</h3>\n        <p>Face an AI opponent in a neon cyber card table for <strong>012 three-lane matrix combat</strong>. Each round you receive cards, deploy them to lanes 0 / 1 / 2, contest power, chip away at HP, and win by defeating the opponent first.</p>\n        <h3>🕹️ Steps (each round)</h3>\n        <ol>\n                  <li><strong>Pick a card:</strong> Tap one of the large hand cards below (it glows)</li>\n                  <li><strong>Pick a lane:</strong> Tap the “Deploy here” zone under LINE 0 / 1 / 2</li>\n                  <li>You can also <strong>tap a lane first, then a hand card</strong> — either order works</li>\n                  <li>Tap a deployed card to <strong>return it to hand</strong></li>\n                  <li>After deploying, tap <strong>“Confirm Deploy”</strong> to fight the AI</li>\n                  <li>Lazy mode: <strong>“Full Meal”</strong> auto-fills all three lanes</li>\n        </ol>\n        <h3>⚔️ Battle Mechanics</h3>\n        <ul>\n                  <li><strong>Lane Resonance:</strong> Matching card value to lane number (e.g. 0 on LINE 0) grants +45% power</li>\n                  <li><strong>Full Meal:</strong> One card per lane covering 0, 1, and 2 → damage ×1.8 this round</li>\n                  <li><strong>Card tiers:</strong> S / A / B differ in power; S gets an extra bonus</li>\n                  <li><strong>Win COMBO:</strong> Winning 2+ lanes in a row triggers combo FX and bonus score</li>\n        </ul>\n        <h3>⏱️ Deploy Timer</h3>\n        <ul>\n                  <li><strong>Easy:</strong> 28s per round; AI plays conservatively</li>\n                  <li><strong>Normal:</strong> 20s; AI contests resonance lanes</li>\n                  <li><strong>Hard:</strong> 15s; AI often uses Full Meal</li>\n                  <li><strong>Extreme:</strong> 12s; high-intensity AI play</li>\n                  <li>When time runs out, combat confirms with your current deploy</li>\n        </ul>\n        <h3>🏆 Ranked Grades</h3>\n        <ul>\n                  <li><strong>S:</strong> Fast deploy + high combo + Full Meal tactics</li>\n                  <li><strong>A:</strong> Consistently win most lanes</li>\n                  <li><strong>B:</strong> Narrow victory</li>\n        </ul>",
