      "helpClose": "✕ Close",
      "helpBack": "Back to Menu",
      "helpHtml": "<h3>🎯 Objective</h3>\n        <p>Pilot your void fighter through a three-lane abyss corridor in an endless dash. Dodge obstacles, weave through lasers, collect energy orbs to sustain your combo multiplier, survive as many waves as possible, and earn a high grade.</p>\n        <h3>🕹️ Controls</h3>\n        <ul>\n          <li><strong>A / D</strong> or <strong>← / →</strong>: Switch left / center / right lane</li>\n          <li><strong>Space</strong>: Void dash (pass through obstacles, has cooldown)</li>\n          <li><strong>Touch swipe</strong>: Swipe left/right to switch lanes</li>\n          <li><strong>ESC / P</strong>: Pause game</li>\n        </ul>\n        <h3>⚡ Obstacle Types</h3>\n        <ul>\n          <li><strong>Energy barrier (cyan):</strong> Blocks one lane — dodge or dash through</li>\n          <li><strong>Pulse laser (purple):</strong> Sweeps one or two lanes — watch the warning flash</li>\n          <li><strong>Drifting mine (pink):</strong> Moves between lanes — timing is unpredictable</li>\n        </ul>\n        <h3>👾 BOSS Waves (every 5 waves)</h3>\n        <ul>\n          <li><strong>Wave 5:</strong> Triple laser sweep — lasers alternate to seal lanes</li>\n          <li><strong>Wave 10:</strong> Barrier wall — consecutive barrier rows need precise dashes</li>\n          <li><strong>Wave 15+:</strong> Abyss storm — mines and lasers intertwine</li>\n        </ul>\n        <h3>💎 Items & Systems</h3>\n        <ul>\n          <li><strong>Energy orbs:</strong> Raise combo multiplier (up to ×5); decays if not collected</li>\n          <li><strong>Shield core:</strong> Absorbs one hit — shown as a purple aura</li>\n          <li><strong>HP:</strong> 3 points — hitting an obstacle costs 1</li>\n          <li><strong>Grades:</strong> S ≥ 50000 · A ≥ 30000 · B ≥ 15000 · C ≥ 5000 · D below</li>\n        </ul>\n        <h3>⚙️ Settings</h3>\n        <ul>\n          <li>From the main menu or in-game via <strong>⚙ Settings</strong>, adjust keyboard move range and lane smoothness</li>\n          <li><strong>Move range Small + smoothness Slow:</strong> Default — one lane per keypress, ~0.46s lane switch</li>\n        </ul>\n        <h3>⚙️ Difficulty</h3>\n        <ul>\n          <li><strong>Casual:</strong> Slower speed, lower spawn rate — good for beginners</li>\n          <li><strong>Standard:</strong> Balanced challenge</li>\n          <li><strong>Abyss:</strong> Extreme speed and dense obstacles — higher combo rewards</li>\n        </ul>",
